<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
  <title>::: ChristmasFuture Email :::</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
  <style type="text/css">
  <!--
  html, body {
    margin:10px;
  }
  body {
    background: #FFF;
    font: 12px/16px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    text-align: left; /* this is asking IE to centre the container ;) */
  }
  
  -->
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div style="text-align:left;width:496px;margin:auto;">

<p>Hello <%=h @gift.to_name? ? @gift.to_name : @gift.to_email %>,</p>

<p>You have been given a ChristmasFuture gift by <a href="mailto:<%= @gift.email %>"><%=h @gift.name? ? @gift.name : @gift.email %></a>.</p>

<% if @gift.ecard? %><%= image_tag "http://#{@host}#{@gift.ecard}", :alt => "" %><% end %>

<% if @gift.message? %>
<p>Their message to you:</p>
<p><%=h @gift.message %></p>
<% end %>

<hr />

<p>Please click on the following link to open your gift so that you can help to change the world.<br />
<%= @url + "?code=#{@gift.pickup_code}" %></p>

<p>If that does not work for you, copy and paste the following link into your web browser and enter your pickup code:<br />
<%= @url %></p>

<p>Pickup Code: <%=h @gift.pickup_code %></p>

<p>Thanks,<br />
<strong>The ChristmasFuture Team</strong></p>

</div>
</body>
</html>